Sentencas: In this paper, we investigate the electrochemical behaviours of solid oxide fuel cells employing Y-doped BaZrO3 (BYZ) thin films as electrolyte.
Titulo: Pulsed laser deposition of Y-doped BaZrO3 thin film as electrolyte for low temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Nano-porous substrate supported thin film solid oxide fuel cells were fabricated with BYZ electrolyte of various thicknesses deposited by pulsed laser deposition.
Titulo: Pulsed laser deposition of Y-doped BaZrO3 thin film as electrolyte for low temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Higher open circuit voltage (OCV) was achieved from the fuel cell with thicker electrolyte which can block more pinholes propagated from the porous substrate.
Titulo: Pulsed laser deposition of Y-doped BaZrO3 thin film as electrolyte for low temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: At 450 degrees C, the OCV and maximum power density of the cell with 1.34 mu m-thick BYZ electrolyte was about 1.1 V and 21 mW/cm(2), respectively.
Titulo: Pulsed laser deposition of Y-doped BaZrO3 thin film as electrolyte for low temperature solid oxide fuel cells

Sentencas: Electrochemical impedance spectroscopy was carried out to reveal phenomena inside the fuel cell.
Titulo: Pulsed laser deposition of Y-doped BaZrO3 thin film as electrolyte for low temperature solid oxide fuel cells
